shared. This kind of technology is already found in MacOS X (branded
&#39, Rendezvous&#39, , &#39, Bonjour&#39, and sometimes &#39, ZeroConf&#39, ) and is very
convenient.");

  script_tag(name:"affected", value:"'avahi' package(s) on Fedora 38.");

